ffff5c268f81ef50 (&dev->lock){+.+.}-{3:3}, at: phy_attach_direct+0x17c/0x3a0 [libphy]

but task is already holding lock:
ffffaef6496cb518 (rtnl_mutex){+.+.}-{3:3}, at: rtnetlink_rcv_msg+0x154/0x560

